name: WAS Odyssey Kassandra
description:
Assassin's Creed Odyssey's Kassandra

Dataset Preperation:

  1. Manually crop to artistic appeal

  2. Downscale to 512x512

  3. Upscale 4x with Gigapixel or Upscayl (usually gigapixel for face restore)

  4. Downscale to 512x512 (again)

  5. Profit from much cleaner images, especially in regard to jagged boundaries from game images

modelVersions.name: ACKass1
modelVersions.description: Kassandra is a little like New Lara Croft, where a lot of material incorporates face dirt, or wear of some sort (sun damage for example), so using modifiers like cute/young/beautiful etc work well. Additionally using negative modifiers like "blemishes, marks, pocks, dirt" help.
